data.description: Welcome to 306 Windcrest Dr, a stunning fully renovated home offering luxury living in the heart of San Antonio. This spacious 3498 sq ft home boasts 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living.    As you step inside, you'll be greeted by luxurious vinyl flooring that sets the tone for the entire home. The open kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring a long high-grade granite countertop perfect for meal prep and entertaining.    The high ceilings and abundant natural lighting create a bright and airy atmosphere throughout the home, enhancing the sense of space and comfort.    Upstairs, the primary suite offers a private retreat with its own balcony overlooking the backyard oasis. Relax and unwind as you take in the serene views of the pool, spa, and landscaped grounds.    Speaking of the backyard, it truly is an oasis unto itself. The luxury-style pool and spa are the focal points, featuring a sun deck, cascade waterfall, and lap pool. The spacious 14x14 spa is perfect for entertaining guests and friends, offering a tranquil space to enjoy warm summer days and cool evenings.    Located in central San Antonio, this home offers easy access to the airport, just 10 minutes away, as well as downtown and the Pearl, both a quick 15-minute drive. Take advantage of the amenities, including the nearby Windcrest Golf Course and neighborhood pool, for added recreation and leisure.    Schedule your showing today and experience luxury living at its finest!
